# Cloudflare Pages — clean URLs
# These rules let /services serve services.html, etc.
# Cloudflare Pages handles .html extension stripping automatically,
# but these explicit rules cover edge cases and old SPA hash routes.

# Redirect old SPA hash-based routes to clean URLs
/#accueil       /           301
/#services      /services   301
/#tarification  /tarification 301
/#loi-16        /loi-16     301
/#blog          /blog       301
/#contact       /contact    301

# 404 fallback — serve 404.html if it exists, otherwise Cloudflare default
# /404            /404.html   200
